data.description: Own this historic, registered landmark in the heart of Cottonwood with a detached VRBO Casita. Completed in 1939 and made of river stone and historic artifacts (check out the fireplace!), the Luther White House is minutes from Old Town, the river, hiking trails, and shopping. Zoned R-4, the main house and Casita each have their own charm, nestled on this three-lot property with room for more homes. Enjoy your private artesian well recently quality tested by ADEQ; drink from the tap and never worry about high water bills. Recent upgrades include new roof, kitchen appliances, and mini-split in casita. The main house has a master-cooled, thermostat-controlled, evaporative system throughout installed in 2021. Fully enclosed property with access from back alley and a root cellar!  See ''more.' Plenty of off-street parking for an RV or camper, and a great veranda with a privacy screen of passionflower vines.  Also listed as Multi-family, MLS# 535004.
